LEVEL 20 TALENT

talent 1
250 life 3.5 life regen and 12% magic resist

talent 2
15 damage 6% spellamp and 12 attack speed


PASSIVE D OR F
Dwarft Might
increase overall stats

life bonus 2% 4% 6% 8%
life regen 1 1.5 2 2.5
spell amp 4% 5% 6% 7%
Strenght 6 7 8 9
magic resist 5% 10%
Muradin will get 1 armor for every 45 str he got

Talent level 25 Upgrade Dwarft Might
double all stats
reduce how much strenght Muradin need for armor by 5

add a new modifier Thunder Hammer
every basic attack, Muradin Release a Chain Lightning dealing 10 physical damage plus 5% of strenght
that jump up to 5 target


SPELL Q
Storm Bolt
deal Heavy damage to a target stunning them and reducing magic resist and armor also pushing the target back

damage 5 20 35 50 plus 40% of strenght -damage type MAGICAL-
cast range 700
push force 600
magic resist lost 7% 9% 11% 13%
armor lost 1 2 3 4
stun duration 2 3 4 5 last half on bosses
cooldown 8 10 12 14
mana cost 75 plus 2% 3% 4% 5% of max mana

talent level 10 upgrade Storm Bolt
increase damage by 20
increase strenght scaling by 12%
increase cast range by 300
increase push force by 100
increase the magic resist lost by 5%
stun duration last full on bosses as well

add a new modifier Violent Bolt
after hiting the target it will send other storm bolt to near enemy in a radius of 350
of the explosion of the first one and dealing full damage to the other target as well
if there is no one around storm bolt damage change to pure and deal 3% of the target max life
as damage


SPELL W
Thunder Clap
Muradin Smash the ground, dealing damage and slowing attack speed and movement speed. The more enemy hit
by this spell the more damage it deal

damage 12 15 18 21 plus 20% of strenght -damage type PURE-
radius 320 340 360 380
attack speed lost 15 20 25 30
movement speed lost 10% 16% 22% 28%
bonus damage per enemy 1 2 3 4
debuff duration 3 4 5 6
cooldown 9
mana cost 70 110 140 170 plus 1% of max mana

talent level 10 Upgrade Thunder Clap
increase damage by 10
increase strenght scaling by 10%
increase radius by 60
increase bonus damage per enemy at all level to 5 -NOTE- the way i mean that, it get 5 damage for level 1 2 3 and 4

add a new mofidier Hammer of Thunder
went Muradin do Thunder Clap for every enemy hit he will get 3 bonus damage for 5 second
and Thunder Clap deal 2% of the current life of the enemy as bonus damage he also heal for 1% of is
max life per enemy hit


SPELL E
Strenght of the Mountain
Muradin next attack will deal bonus damage and increase attack speed as well, The last hit will deal increase damage and do cleave
attack

damage bonus 12 14 16 18
attack speed bonus 45
number of attack 2 3 4 5
last hit damage increase 20 28 34 42
last hit cleave damage 40% 70% 100% 130%
radius of cleave 280
no mana cost
cooldown 70 65 60 55

talent level 15 upgrade Strenght of the Mountain
increase damage by 4
increase attack speed by 15
increase last hit damage by 10
increase cleave radius by 50

add a new modifier Mountain of Fire
went landing the last hit, Muradin will Create a Mountain that deal 30 pure damage per second in a 420 radius around it
the mountain last 6 second, any enemy that die during Strenght of the Mountain will reduce the cooldown Strenght of the Mountain
by 3


PASSIVE D OR F
Dwarft Mastery
increase Muradin damage and attack speed also give a chance to bash the target dealing damage and stunning them

bonus damage 3 5 7 9
bonus attack speed 5 8 11 14
bash chance 15% 16% 17% 18%
bash damage 15 -damage type PHYSICAL-
Strenght scaling 20% 35% 50% 65%
armor scaling 25%
bash duration 0.3 0.4 0.5 0.6 last half on bosses

talent level 15 upgrade Dwarft Mastery
increase bonus attack speed by 6
increase bash damage by 5
increase strenght scaling by 25%

add a new modifier Mountain Hammer
every time Muradin bash the next bash get 5 increase damage, the buff last 6 second after 4 stack of Mountain Hammer
the next bash will do pure damage and increase muradin attack speed by 50 for 5 second, this effect got 14 second cooldown


ULTIMATE R
Avatar
